{"id":3192,"date":"2020-03-03T11:07:27","date_gmt":"2020-03-03T04:07:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=3192"},"modified":"2020-03-27T12:01:51","modified_gmt":"2020-03-27T05:01:51","slug":"cong-trinh-rem-cua-nha-chi-huong-tai-trau-quy-gia-lam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/cong-trinh-rem-cua-nha-chi-huong-tai-trau-quy-gia-lam.html","title":{"rendered":"C\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh r\u00e8m c\u1eeda nh\u00e0 Ch\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Tr\u00e2u Q\u00f9y, Gia L\u00e2m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">C\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh r\u00e8m c\u1eeda t\u1ea1i Gia L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng ty R\u00e8m c\u1eeda Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh gi\u00e0nh t\u00e2m huy\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-han-quoc\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">M\u1eabu r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/a> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ea3i voan tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u00ean ch\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u00f3 tone m\u00e0u ghi s\u00e1ng cho c\u1ea3 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i v\u00e0 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng. H\u00e3y chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ch\u1ecb ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-3200 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/161499a74ff4b4aaede5-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1237\" height=\"928\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/161499a74ff4b4aaede5-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/161499a74ff4b4aaede5-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/161499a74ff4b4aaede5-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/161499a74ff4b4aaede5-1067x800.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1237px) 100vw, 1237px\" title=\"\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u00e0u ghi cho c\u1eeda c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u1edbn<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3204\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3204\" style=\"width: 1254px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-3204\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-cau-vong-cho-cua-so-nho\" width=\"1254\" height=\"1672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/cded3b13ed40161e4f51.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1254px) 100vw, 1254px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3204\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">rem-cau-vong-cho-cua-so-nho<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng cao c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i Gia L\u00e2m<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i th\u00ec n\u00f3 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t. Do v\u1eady, R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho ch\u1ecb b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp m\u00e0u ghi s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd lo b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i mode<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3198\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/4689d639006afb34a27b-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-vai-chong-nang-tot\" width=\"1320\" height=\"991\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/4689d639006afb34a27b-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/4689d639006afb34a27b-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/4689d639006afb34a27b-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/4689d639006afb34a27b-1067x800.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1320px) 100vw, 1320px\" title=\"\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1eabu m\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb9p<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Trang b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m cho c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 hay c\u1eeda l\u1edbn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ee5i, gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb h\u01a1n cho m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh.Theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec ch\u1ecb mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m l\u00ean s\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb9p, m\u00fai to \u0111\u1ec1u, n\u00ean r\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n cho ch\u1ecb ki\u1ec3u may Or\u00ea \u0111\u1ee5c l\u1ed7. V\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u may n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi th\u1ee3 may ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kim, m\u0169i ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng m\u00fai sao cho \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3205\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-vai-chong-nang-tot\" width=\"1315\" height=\"1753\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/d36eaed1788283dcda93.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1315px) 100vw, 1315px\" title=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><em>Ki\u1ec3u may ore t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u00fai s\u00f3ng r\u00e8m \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cao c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 l\u1edbp voan tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. L\u1edbp voan tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ec3 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00eam cho b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9, ng\u0103n b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3196\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3196\" style=\"width: 1330px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-3196\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-vai-hai-lop-sieu-dep\" width=\"1330\" height=\"1773\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/7ecc5b138d40761e2f51.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1330px) 100vw, 1330px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3196\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">rem-vai-hai-lop-sieu-dep<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa l\u1edbp voan nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m \u0111\u1eb9p th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n cao c\u1ea5p \u0111i k\u00e8m. B\u1ed9 thanh ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n nh\u00f4m s\u01a1n t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, ch\u1ed1ng m\u00f2n, d\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m hai l\u1edbp si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3202\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3202\" style=\"width: 1348px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-3202\" style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-vai-hai-lop-sieu-dep\" width=\"1348\" height=\"1798\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bf93b758610b9a55c31a.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1348px) 100vw, 1348px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3202\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">rem-vai-hai-lop-sieu-dep<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">B\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n thanh nh\u00f4m t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n cao c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1o cho b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m s\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cao c\u1ea5p<\/span><\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng che n\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Ch\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Gia L\u00e2m c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7, Ch\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 tin d\u00f9ng r\u00e8m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng Modero c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100% \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 nh\u1ecf<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3193\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3193\" style=\"width: 1313px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-3193\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"rem-cau-vong-han-quoc\" width=\"1313\" height=\"1751\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/0b2be9f73fa4c4fa9db5.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1313px) 100vw, 1313px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3193\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">rem-cau-vong-han-quoc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Modero cho c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 nh\u1ecf<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 l\u1edbp \u0111an xen gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp l\u01b0\u1edbi trong su\u1ed1t t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m r\u00e8m \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i d\u1ec7t t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng 100%, L\u1edbp l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1edbi cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i cao, ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e3y, \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e